name: le_dahye (이다혜)
description:
First model i've ever made, wanted to give a try to textual inversions, but resemblance to the real person is quite limited despite my efforts.

Used 10 pictures to train, only face

Works best with Lofi model (https://civitai.com/models/9052)

Untick "Restore Faces" for better results

I noticed better results with dpm++ 2s a karras

The training is a bit baked, so it might ends up with 2 heads sometimes.
